General.Name: Gabriel Holding
General.Description: Gabriel Holding A/S develops, manufactures, and sells upholstery fabrics, components, upholstered surfaces, and related products and services in Denmark and internationally. The company operates through two segments, Fabrics and Letting of office facilities. The Fabrics segment offers furniture fabrics and related textile products to manufacturers and customers in upholstered furniture, seating, and upholstered surfaces. The Letting of office facilities segment lets office premises in Aalborg. Gabriel Holding A/S was founded in 1851 and is headquartered in Aalborg, Denmark.
